<br>
'The best frontal damage dealers'<br>
<br>
Whats the point of being the best frontal damage dealers if you cannot actually stand infront of the mob to deal your damage?<br>
<br>
Other then that which is taking it to extremes for the joke of it, I do actually agree with Thott.<br>
<br>
You guys have to accept that this is part of the 'Mitigation re-balancing' same as our triple attack and improved damage table at 55 and 60 were a part of the 'damage re-balancing'.<br>
<br>
I don't believe we will be nerfed that badly, I am certainly not happy about it, but I Am by far unhappier about the fact that they intend to nerf Mod Rod 2 which will in turn screw every guild in the game over.<br>
<br>
An encounter should not be based on how many clerics/druids you have turn up, there should never be a time in the game when 50 odd people have to go home or go xp because 2 clerics didn't log in, now Mod Rod 2 gave the ability to do things with less clerics then before, thats all, it doesn't make it ANY easier at all, it doesn't make the mob hit for less, it doesn't make your melee hit for more, all it does is give your clerics a chance to cast CH more, meaning instead of needing another 2 clerics you just needed one magician.<br>
<br>
Which meant instead of 50 people doing nothing you could go raid something.<br>
<br>
I am more pissed by that then any proposed change to Mod Rods. <p><img src="http://www.kefen.btinternet.co.uk/Sig1.JPG"></center><center><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=368612"> My Equipment </A></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#cccccc><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/uatroxiscrotalus.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Atroxis Crotalus</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/anim_1.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Disciple</span><br>  Posts: 266<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(10/13/02 7:30:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=33026.topic&index=32>Reply</a>    <br>ezSupporter<br> <BR><img src=http://darksev-2.netfirms.com/small.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Something useful to complain about</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><b><i>Quote:</i></b><hr> <br>
